<template><h1 id="搭建环境" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#搭建环境" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 搭建环境</h1>
<h2 id="搭建-vite-项目" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#搭建-vite-项目" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 搭建 Vite 项目</h2>
<div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token comment"># 查看 npm 版本</span>
<span class="token function">npm</span> -v
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br></div></div><p><a href="https://cn.vitejs.dev/guide/#scaffolding-your-first-vite-project" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vite 官网<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></p>
<p>创建项目</p>
<div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token comment"># npm 7+, extra double-dash is needed:</span>
